long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Multilanguage Wizard for Squarespace domain registration (dns) and then google website management : 

It is a tool that will help you register a domain name through SquareSpace Domains and then prepare your website with Google services and google website management tools that aims to help people with little knowledge of web technologies.
This plugin works as a setup wizard in 42 languages. First of all, it directs you to the page where you will register a new domain name, and then, with simpler explanations from this page, it directs you to the page where you will prepare your website after this domain name registration.
You can use this plugin for free. We hope that you will produce useful services and products for people with your new website. With this version, you can use this tool especially for google sites editor.

We intend to improve the explanations and directions in this first version to help you more in future versions.
